These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, mystery, action, sports
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, taxi, trike, boat
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, blood-red, yellow, fuchsia
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, traveling, video-games, reading
 1. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 2. the person watching musical movies is in an even position##4
 3. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 4. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 5. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
 6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
 7. the person who likes blood-red is the person watching action movies##1
 8. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person driving the boat##2
10. the person watching musical movies is the person who's hobby is reading##1
11. the person driving the trike is the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre          | action  | musical    | sports    | mystery   |
| Transport   | taxi     | helicopter   | trike       | boat    |
| Color   | blood-red | ivory | fuchsia    | yellow |
| Hobby           | traveling | reading       | singing | video-games     |

