.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, satire, time-travel, drama
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, baccarat, siglo, blend
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, snowmobile, taxi, quad-bike
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, blue, lavender, mauve
 1. the blend-smoker is in an even position##4
 2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
 3. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 5. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
 7. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 8. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person who likes red##3
 9. the person driving the taxi is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person watching time-travel movies is in an odd position##4
11. the person driving the taxi is the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre          | zombie  | satire    | time-travel     | drama       |
| Cigar         | siglo | blend | bluemaster   | baccarat |
| Transport   | taxi | jet-ski   | snowmobile   | quad-bike    |
| Color         | lavender | mauve  | red | blue   |

