.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, tiparillo, alhambra, swisher
4 different games are played: poker, billiard, backgammon, snooker
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, baking, camping, cooking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, r&b, classical, soul
 1. the old-henry-smoker is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
 2. the person who's hobby is baking is the person playing backgammon##1
 3. the old-henry-smoker is on the left or right of the alhambra-smoker##3
 4. the person playing poker is on the right of the fan of soul##1
 5. the tiparillo-smoker is the person playing snooker##1
 6. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
 7. the fan of pop is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 8. the person playing snooker is in an even position##4
 9. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
10. the fan of pop is the alhambra-smoker##1
11. the old-henry-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Cigar      | old-henry | alhambra   | swisher    | tiparillo      |
| Game           | backgammon | poker | billiard | snooker     |
| Hobby   | baking      | cooking   | photography   | camping |
| Music-Genre           | soul         | pop       | classical  | r&b       |

