.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
4 different games are played: billiard, domino, poker, backgammon
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, december, february, may
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, havana, bongani, blend
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, disaster, satire, action
 1. the person playing billiard is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 2. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
 4. the havana-smoker is in an even position##4
 5. the person playing domino is the person watching action movies##1
 6. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 7. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
 9. the person watching satire movies is the havana-smoker##1
10. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
11. the person playing poker is the person who's birthday is in may##1
12. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Game   | backgammon       | poker   | billiard   | domino   |
| Birthday       | december        | may | november    | february       |
| Cigar      | blend | havana    | bongani  | old-henry |
| Movie-Genre      | disaster  | satire  | martial-arts | action    |

