.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, may, july, june
House: craftsman, townhouse, victorian, farmhouse
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, thriller, crime, time-travel
4 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog, rat, goat
 1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the victorian house is between the owner of the dog and the person who's birthday is in june##2
 3. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 4. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 5. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
 6. the craftsman house is in an even position##4
 7. the person who's birthday is in may is the person watching zombie movies##1
 8. the victorian house is the person watching thriller movies##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
10. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
11. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
12. the farmhouse house is on the left of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Birthday    | july    | june      | october          | may    |
| House   | townhouse | farmhouse       | victorian | craftsman |
| Movie-Genre     | time-travel     | crime      | thriller     | zombie |
| Pet   | hedgehog   | goat | rat        | dog   |

