.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechaniccher, architect, journalist, mechanic
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, red, azure, ivory
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, balloon-flower, poppy, rose
House: farmhouse, craftsman, victorian, tower
 1. the person who likes azure is on the left of the mechaniccher##1
 2. the mechaniccher is on the left or right of the architect##3
 3. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person who likes red##1
 4. the journalist is on the left or right of the architect##3
 5. the mechaniccher is in an odd position##4
 6. the person who growsrose is between the victorian house and the person who growsballoon-flower##2
 7. the person who growspoppy is the person who likes azure##1
 8. the architect is the person who likes azure##1
 9. the craftsman house is on the far right##1
10. the farmhouse house is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job      | journalist  | architect    | mechaniccher       | mechanic       |
| Color          | ivory    | azure | red | chestnut     |
| Flower   | daisy | poppy        | rose    | balloon-flower   |
| House   | farmhouse  | victorian      | tower    | craftsman |

