The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, singing, gardening, photography
 1. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 2. the designer is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the nurse##3
 5. the person drinking juice is on the left of the cottage house##1
 6. the dressmaker is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 7. the art-deco house is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 8. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
10. the architect is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
12. the tower house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4      |
