.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-8::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, punk, blues, gospel
There 4 different types of food: pepper, strawberry, spinach, corn
4 different games are played: poker, go, backgammon, billiard
House: cottage, gothic-revival, palace, cape-cod
 1. the cape-cod house is in an odd position##4
 2. the cottage house is between the cape-cod house and the palace house##2
 3. the person playing poker is on the left of the fan of blues##1
 4. the person eating spinach is in an odd position##4
 5. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 6. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
 7. the palace house is on the left of the fan of blues##1
 8. the fan of punk is on the left of the person playing go##1
 9. the cottage house is between the person playing poker and the person eating strawberry##2
10. the fan of punk is on the left of the cottage house##1
11. the fan of gospel is in an even position##4
12. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre         | punk  | blues    | reggae    | gospel |
| Food   | spinach   | pepper       | strawberry  | corn    |
| Game   | poker | go | backgammon | billiard   |
| House           | palace    | cottage        | cape-cod   | gothic-revival    |

