There 4 different types of food: pineapple, mango, carrot, kiwi
4 different pets are kept: bird, mouse, rabbit, frog
 1. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
 2. the person eating carrot is the owner of the frog##1
 3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the social-worker##1
 4. the person eating carrot is the person playing billiard##1
 5. the architect is on the right of the videographer##1
 6. the dressmaker is in an odd position##4
 7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
 8. the person eating kiwi is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
 9. the person playing scrabble is in an even position##4
10. the person playing canasta is between the dressmaker and the person eating carrot##2
11. the person eating mango is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
12. the person eating kiwi is on the left or right of the person eating mango##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4     |
| Job   | videographer | architect  | dressmaker      | social-worker   |
| Game   | billiard  | canasta  | snooker  | scrabble     |
| Food   | carrot | kiwi | mango | pineapple |
| Pet     | frog  | rabbit  | mouse   | bird     |

