.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, electrician, chef, dancer
City: venice, prague, rome, hamburg
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, alhambra, swisher, bolivar
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, quad-bike, ship, scooter
 1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
 2. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the electrician##3
 3. the blend-smoker is on the left of the dancer##1
 4. the alhambra-smoker is in an even position##4
 5. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the analyst##1
 6. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 7. the person traveling to prague is on the far right##1
 8. the swisher-smoker is on the far right##1
 9. the alhambra-smoker is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
10. the person driving the ship is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
11. the bolivar-smoker is in an odd position##4
12. the person traveling to venice is the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Job      | chef       | electrician | analyst        | dancer        |
| City         | hamburg | rome       | venice | prague |
| Cigar   | bolivar     | alhambra        | blend    | swisher      |
| Transport         | quad-bike     | ship    | scooter | airplane   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, 7up, cola, juice
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, aquamarine, grey, mauve
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, lily, azalea, bellflower
4 different pets are kept: pony, rat, turtle, snake
 1. the person drinking juice is the person who growsazalea##1
 2. the person who growsazalea is between the person who likes apricot and the person who likes mauve##2
 3. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the person who growsaconite##3
 4. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
 5. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is the person who growslily##1
 7. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
 8. the person who likes mauve is in an even position##4
 9. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the person who growsaconite##3
10. the person who likes apricot is in an even position##4
11. the person who likes apricot is on the far right##1
12. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who likes grey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | 7up      | tea | juice     | cola        |
| Color   | grey | mauve  | aquamarine     | apricot |
| Flower         | lily    | aconite | azalea      | bellflower |
| Pet     | snake | rat     | turtle | pony       |

 